<p style="text-align: justify;">Thomas Lemar was heavily scouted by Liverpool for Coutinho replacement as he is familiar to play as winger/forward for 4-4-2 system and also can play in 3-man midfield. We were also told that Liverpool made a bid of more than 90 million euros at the end of transfer window but deal could not happen.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>2. Julian Draxler</strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-427" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-5-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="541" height="361" />

