<p style="text-align: justify;">Julian Draxler was previously approached by Jurgen Klopp but he chooses PSG instead of Liverpool. Due to his versatility for playing as central midfield or winger in front line, many scouts and pundits believes that he is the ideal one to replace Coutinho at Liverpool.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>3. Malcom</strong></p>
