<p style="text-align: justify;">France was the group leader in group A winning 7 games 2 draws and one loss. On the sixth round of the qualifier, France lost against Sweden the final score of the game was 2-1 where Giroud scored for France. The best performance of France was against the Netherlands with the final score of 4 â€“ 0 where Griezmann, Lemar, and Mbappe scored.</p>
